title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Bountiful Bounty Targets
content:
It’s time to get bounty hunting.

Your new Bail Office’s computer comes installed with the Bail Enforcement System all set up with targets ready to be secured. Select a target from the four available and secure them alive for the highest rewards.

Targets will be updated regularly. If you happen to accidentally eliminate your target, your cut won’t be as bountiful. Invite some friends to help you for their own chance at a reward.
